Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:39.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}The Plight of the Riku Clan!\NThe Lurking Hero Awaits in the Shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.98,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,They're raining down, one after the other.{Changed the timing here a bit, as that first sound he makes isn't really part of the sentence. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:57.72,Main,Boo,0,0,0,,Gramps, big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:01:59.20,Main,Boo,0,0,0,,It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:01.17,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,So you were thrown down here too, Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.58,Main,Boo,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.88,Main,Boo,0,0,0,,A mountain of toys and rubbish?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:10.44,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,That's what I wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:13.45,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,Another one's gonna fall, you should move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.18,Gladiator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(374,562)\fad(100,0)}Former Gladiator Ricky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:19.82,Main,Ricky,0,0,0,,I didn't know that such a large scrapyard existed underneath the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:25.73,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,If I'm mistaken, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.73,Gladiator,,0,0,180,,{\fad(100,0)}Dressrosa Squad Captain\NTank Lepanto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.73,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,{\an8}But I've got a nagging feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.54,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:36.64,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Might you possibly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:41.24,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,His Highness, King Riku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.91,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,King Riku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:47.98,Main,Abdullah,0,0,0,,King Riku? That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.24,Main,Abdullah,0,0,0,,Isn't he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:55.22,Main,Jeet,0,0,0,,Speaking of Dressrosa's former King,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:59.16,Main,Jeet,0,0,0,,I heard that he went crazy and was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:07.36,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,After having fallen so far,\Nthere really isn't any point in hiding it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.50,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Indeed I am him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:17.44,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,But please do not call me a king, Commander Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:24.03,Captions,,0,0,180,,{\fad(300,300)}Former King of Dressrosa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.03,Main,Gladiator,0,0,5,,{\fad(0,300)}It's King Riku.{It's Garp Oji-chan with a new haircut >_>}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.67,Captions,,0,0,250,,{\fad(200,320)}Riku Doldo III\N(Rebecca's grandfather)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:28.05,Main,Gladiator,0,0,5,,You were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:34.09,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you were safe, King Riku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:37.62,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,I am only an old man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:41.98,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,A sinful old man who couldn't even save his only granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.02,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,It has been such a long time. {Xemnas: Can the editor change the wording of this to make it sound more formal? Mainly because Elizabello says the same thing a bit later, but since they're both kings and his tone is much lighter and less formal, I guess I just wanted to make a distinction between the two.}{Seconding this request. This sentence really should sound more formal, though I can't think of a way to do so myself.[/not a native speaker] -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:47.51,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.21,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Doflamingo's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:52.62,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,There's no need to say it. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.75,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,You were watching over Viola.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:04:01.83,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,How could I ever doubt a man with as much honor as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:04.66,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,It must have been a difficult decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.36,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,No, compared to your troubles...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.90,Main,Elizabello,0,0,0,,Oh my, so you were King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.77,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Oh, the king of Prodence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.30,Main,Elizabello,0,0,0,,That really takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:20.96,Main,Elizabello,0,0,0,,You have saved my country from crisis, many times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.44,Main,Elizabello,0,0,0,,I'm glad you are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.84,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:26.85,Main,Elizabello,0,0,0,,Ever since you disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:31.53,Main,Elizabello,0,0,0,,there's been a power imbalance in the surrounding countries, resulting in constant war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.82,Main,Elizabello,0,0,0,,I'm really tired of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.02,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,Hold up, Elizabello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:40.93,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,You may be tired of it, but if someone's laughing, someone's also crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:48.40,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,Someone has been making a massive\Nprofit from instigating all the wars!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:52.30,Main,Boo,0,0,0,,By supplying weapons to all those warring countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:01.22,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,The broker is a man named Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:04.29,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Which is Doflamingo's alias in the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:09.58,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,But we don't know where those weapons are being made or stored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:16.75,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Our Flower Country has been losing badly in the war because of those weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:20.63,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,Our entry in the colosseum's tournament was merely part of our investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:28.61,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,The Happou Navy was ordered by our king to destroy the weapons factory. That's our true goal. {Cecil: I cant remember if we use Happo or Happou}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:33.37,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,King Riku, because you committed that act which allowed Doflamingo to become king,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:36.67,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,many of the neighbouring countries are in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.21,Main,Dagama,0,0,0,,Exactly so, Elizabello-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:44.94,Main,Dagama,0,0,0,,It's true that we owe a lot to Dressrosa for what they have done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:48.60,Main,Dagama,0,0,0,,But your worry for that man is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.82,Main,Dagama,0,0,0,,Right now, the name King Riku-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:53.20,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Shut up, Dagama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:58.73,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,You don't know what really happened on that tragic day ten years ago.    {Isis:didn't a prisoner say "what happened on that night " just an episode ago!! O_O}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.06,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,How dare you speak ill of the king?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.31,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,It's alright, Tank. It doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:08.51,Main,Gladiator,0,0,0,,King Riku, I am also a former soldier of your army.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.27,Main,Gladiator,0,0,0,,As am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:12.82,Main,Gladiator,0,0,0,,Me too, King Riku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:19.36,Main,Gladiator,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.25,Main,Gladiator,0,0,0,,The toys have started moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:25.40,Main,Gladiator,0,0,0,,I thought they were just trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:46.23,Main,Gladiator,0,0,0,,All the former soldiers of Dressrosa and even the toys are bowing down to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.69,Main,Gladiator,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:50.91,Main,Gladiator,0,0,0,,Wasn't King Riku hated by the entire country?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:07:00.77,Main,Hack,0,0,0,,With such a large pitfall here, it seems that there are some secrets hidden underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.29,Main,Hack,0,0,0,,{\i1}With such a large pitfall here, it seems that there are some secrets hidden underground.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.51,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Understood. {Cecil: Would be really unfair to use this person's real name :P}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.20,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Continue with your investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.29,Main,Boo,0,0,0,,Big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.84,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,What the hell's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:16.88,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,What's going on now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.07,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.09,Main,Boo,0,0,0,,Big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.20,Main,Trebol,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.44,Main,Trebol,0,0,0,,It's over now, so you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.26,Main,Trebol,0,0,0,,Do not harm any humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:47.23,Main,Trebol,0,0,0,,And follow the orders of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.38,Main,Trebol,0,0,0,,Make sure you follow these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:56.41,Main,Trebol,0,0,0,,Exit through that door and you'll reach the factory and trade port.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.66,Main,Trebol,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:02.79,Main,Trebol,0,0,0,,No talking! Make sure you work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:09.13,Thoughts,Trebol,0,0,0,,All the participants are powerful, so they won't break very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:11.29,Thoughts,Sai,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:14.31,Thoughts,Sai,0,0,0,,My body won't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.84,Thoughts,Sai,0,0,0,,I can't go against his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:22.65,Thoughts,Sai,0,0,0,,What's just happened to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:25.57,Main,Luffy,0,0,3,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.57,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(200,0)}Colosseum\NPrisoner Gladiator Lodging
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:31.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, who cares about Cabbage?! Show Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:35.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Actually, come to think of it, it's really hard to see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:37.63,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'll cheer her on from somewhere closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.35,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:44.26,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I used to think\Nthis country looked really fun and happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.58,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,but looking at you guys, maybe I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:51.11,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,What you saw was the flowery world of the winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:57.58,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Doflamingo divides the world\Ninto obedient winners and disobedient losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:02.48,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,He's exactly like the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:07.42,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Those who oppose him\Nare losers who get treated like garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:13.58,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Hide the garbage in darkness, and sure,\Nthe country ends up looking perfect from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:18.45,Flashbacks,Man,0,0,0,,Let's go search for treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:27.48,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's just like the country I grew up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:32.12,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Once you start questioning things,\Nyou see that something is wrong in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:35.75,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,We believe that there are even darker secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.46,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,You better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.13,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:58.51,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:08.50,Captions,,0,0,180,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Flower Fields - Riku Royal Fighters Rebellion Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:06.85,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ancient writings say that long ago, our ancestors went out to sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:12.00,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,{\an8}searching for resources that their country didn't possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:18.86,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,But when they were discovered by the big humans, they were brought to the brink of extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.85,Flashbacks,Person,0,0,0,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.48,Flashbacks,Person,0,0,0,,Dwarves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:30.58,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,But one day, the king of Dressrosa,\Na neighbouring country, offered them a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:40.05,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,In exchange for a bit of manual labor, he would offer them the resources they desired and their safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:45.06,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,The name of that king was Donquixote.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:54.65,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,That's the worst part of our history, which continued until 900 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:58.58,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,The age of slavery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:04.98,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,The writings that follow show what the royal family truly were...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:07.45,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,Demons, through and through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:16.46,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,Our people were forced to work day in and day out, deep underground where no one could see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:23.78,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,The big humans lived on the riches and prosperity brought by the Tontatta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:33.77,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,No one knows what happened in the void century but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:39.24,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,800 years ago, a new king was born into Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.51,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Riku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:56.78,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,After hearing of the dwarves' inhumane treatment for the past few hundred years,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:12:03.10,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,it is told that he shed tears and deeply apologized from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:10.17,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,And the next action of the\Nnew king was one of repentance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:19.44,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,He said that we could take anything we needed from this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.87,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,That we didn't need to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:34.23,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,The king called it the work of fairies and calmed the citizens with laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:39.04,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,He successfully created the legend of the fairies in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.77,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,King Riku the First, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:50.01,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,The country led by the kind Riku line even provided support for neighbouring countries in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.54,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,I can't say the country was wealthy and prosperous,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:57.39,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,but it was a wonderful one full of smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:02.31,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,Our ancestors paid tribute to the kind King Riku,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:10.33,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,by turning this country into one of beautiful fields and flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:17.61,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,That is the 800 year long bond between our Tontatta Kingdom and the Riku royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:29.28,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,But after 900 years, the descendant of the Donquixote family, Doflamingo returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:34.66,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,Strangely enough, he is trying to replay our horrible history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:45.27,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,Over 500 of our people, including my daughter Mansherry have fallen prey to his sinister ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:50.41,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,We mustn't let those times repeat themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:52.78,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,We won't let it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.31,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,We'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:59.31,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Indeed, to Dressrosa, and to the Tontatta,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:03.52,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,the Donquixote Family's rule\Nwill only bring suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.86,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,We'll fight alongside our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:13.10,Main,Inhel,0,0,0,,With Usoland on our side, we can't lose. {Xemnas: Went a bit liberal here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:21.50,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,{\i1}Usoland! Usoland! Usoland!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.54,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I was thinking the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:24.98,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,As expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.47,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,King Riku was such a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:33.18,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,He was nice to the bug people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.71,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are you calling bugs?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:37.46,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I meant it in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.32,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then it's okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:40.86,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Captain-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:47.47,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,The female gladiator fighting in the colosseum, is being called King Riku's granddaughter, {Once again, this cannot be here. She is fighting Logan later in the episode and earlier....}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.73,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,and is really being insulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.96,Secondary,Audience,0,0,0,,Drop dead, Rebecca! {Xemnas: This is being said at the same time as Robin's line in the background.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:49.73,Secondary,Audience,0,0,0,,You're the shame of Dressrosa! {Xemnas: Same as previous line}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:53.15,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,The people of this country seem to hate King Riku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:55.42,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I was thinking the same thing! {Exact same phrasing as thirty seconds ago, for the record. -Starfish}{Isis: it's okay since it's the usual Usopp's funny act}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.43,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.08,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,{\i1}Usoland! Usoland! Usoland!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.95,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,On that day, 10 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.95,Secondary,Dwarves,0,0,0,,{\i1}Usoland!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:07.57,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,an incident happened that caused King Riku to lose the country's trust in one night.{Isis: now it comes back to being that night, can someone clarify this .}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:13.36,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Even though the king tried to protect the country all the way until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:19.06,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,The citizens don't know the truth about that incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:28.29,Flashbacks,Soldier,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I couldn't protect your mother. {copy paste from 651}{end copy paste}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:34.66,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,At that time, Doflamingo tried to destroy the Riku blood line, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:42.00,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,I took King Riku's granddaughter Rebecca and continued to run for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.56,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,But, she was eventually captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:50.83,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,And now she is put on show at the colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:59.97,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,I'll gladly lay down my life to protect\N King Riku's integrity and Rebecca's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:04.42,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,I am betting everything on this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.15,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Just why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:18.72,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,I couldn't protect Rebecca's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:27.30,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Never for a second have I forgotten what happened on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:34.02,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Having been turned into a toy, she may no longer remember me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.43,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:11.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:16.61,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Your back's wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:24.84,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,What's this? Rebecca saw her chance and escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:32.83,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Rebecca is scurrying around like a mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:42.56,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,And Rolling Logan is in hot pursuit,\Ntaking down any fighter that gets in his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.98,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,That's cheap, Rebecca! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.84,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Fight and let us see some blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.24,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Damn descendant of King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:06.63,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Your family's pure evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:11.61,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,If you're her father...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.17,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,doesn't that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:15.97,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,since she's King Riku's granddaughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:20.82,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,that... back when you were human, you...{Honestly in this case even I'm getting annoyed by all the trailing-off. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:23.66,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,It all began on that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.62,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.25,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You must be King Riku's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:31.99,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,No, actually it may have started long before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:36.33,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,On the day when that woman, Monet, began working in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:37.70,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Monet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.47,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,The bird-woman from Punk Hazard? {dat memory loss}{Cecil: The way he reacted to seeing her, YESTERDAY, you'd think he's scream his head off right there.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:48.05,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,This country has changed a lot in the past 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:50.56,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Both the land and its people. {Cecil: This is my favourite song from dressrosa, I patiently await for some sort of soundtrack to come out with it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.51,Captions,,0,0,180,,{\fad(500,0)}Dressrosa 10 Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.51,Main,Citizen,0,0,4,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:55.14,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Pirates attacked my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:58.55,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Though since the Riku Royal Army protects us, the damage wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:07.37,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,It hasn't rained in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:11.26,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Yeah. But despite the drought, the flowers haven't wilted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.23,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:14.59,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to the fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.77,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,They protect our flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.22,Main,Child,0,0,0,,I want more food!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.44,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,If you have enough energy left to shout, then you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:28.68,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,We may be poor, but this country is free from war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.88,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:33.93,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Yeah! {...No seriously, this entire sequence just BOTHERS THE CRAP OUT OF ME. I refuse to believe that it could have been as idyllic as they portray it here. -Starfish}{most unrealistic reaction from a kid that's never experienced anything horribly traumatic like that before.}{Sewil: be more grumpy pls}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.53,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,In the 800 years under the Riku Royal Family's rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.19,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,this country has never fought a single war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:43.46,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:46.33,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Indeed. Miraculous, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.85,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Dressrosa was a truly peaceful country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:50.55,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:55.84,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,without warning, a nightmare descended upon the royal palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:58.14,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.28,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Don't shout. Don't call for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.65,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:10.49,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,I am Donquixote Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:16.26,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,The rumors about this pirate Donquixote have caused me some concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:20.43,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Yeah, your worries were spot-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:27.07,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,I am a descendant of the Donquixote family, the old rulers of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:35.65,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,I am the rightful ruler of this kingdom. The king has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:43.39,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,From what I heard, you robbed a transport ship that was carrying tribute for the Celestial Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:47.36,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,and used that money to blackmail the Government into making you a Warlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:53.36,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,They don't know how to deal with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:57.87,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,The fact that I don't fear the Celestial Dragons really worries them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:02.67,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,If you know who I am and what I can do, that simplifies matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:07.68,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,I'll sell you the country for 10,000,000,000 belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.41,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,You'll {\i1}sell{\i0} the country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:16.25,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Normally I'd just take it without giving you this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:21.79,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,If I can use money to avoid bloodshed, then so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:25.33,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,But this country doesn't even {\i1}have{\i0}\N10,000,000,000{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:27.06,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Of course it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:30.37,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,You have until dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:35.08,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,No getting help from other countries. I'm testing your power as king.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:39.21,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,However, you are not to tell your citizens about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:41.72,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,You have two options.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:45.12,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Either avoid a fight by gathering money,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:48.89,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,or fight and see the blood of your subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:52.20,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Choose whichever you prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:22:00.56,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better to fight Doflamingo, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:01.99,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:07.40,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Calling it "fighting" might make it sound nicer, but it would be manslaughter, an inhuman act!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:15.16,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,But even if we try to gather up money, there aren't many rich people in this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:23.49,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,The fact that Dressrosa has been at peace for 800 years proves that we are not beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:26.16,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Don't lower yourself to the level of animals! Be human!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:29.19,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,I will not let people kill each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:30.73,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,We have no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:33.13,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Send troops to all towns in Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:35.93,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,We must gather up 10,000,000,000 belly from this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.93,0:22:40.44,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,If we don't, this will become a kingdom ruled by pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:45.75,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,I'm sure that gathering the money will mean that I'll lose the people's trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:47.68,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,but only for a few hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:51.75,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Once this is all over, I will do whatever I can to make it up to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:55.35,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,That is all we can do.  We can't solve this through lies or stalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:23:02.43,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Keep gathering money for as long as you can! The life of this kingdom depends on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:08.61,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,It's the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:10.07,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,What could they want so late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:11.77,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Isn't that Commander Tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:17.03,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Listen to me, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.03,0:23:20.68,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,I want you to gather all the money you have and bring it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:22.51,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:25.52,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Do you really think the king will let you get away with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:27.72,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,This is an order from the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:32.82,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Quickly! We can't explain our reasons, nor do we have time to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:37.90,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Please, just have faith in King Riku and bring whatever money you have here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:41.10,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,But this is just so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:45.10,Thoughts,Tank,0,0,0,,This is madness! There's no way they'll accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.13,0:23:48.51,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,A Projector Snail?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:50.61,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,To everyone in Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:51.71,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.71,0:23:53.04,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,It's King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:58.52,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,I have a request. It's rather sudden, and so unreasonable you might doubt your hearing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:02.98,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,please don't ask me why I'm doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:05.25,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Please just get whatever money you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:07.83,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,and lend it all to me! {Xemnas: nuance and all}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:10.99,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,The king's bowing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.99,0:24:12.43,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.86,0:24:15.35,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,But why would he ask this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:16.73,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,It's just so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.57,0:24:21.07,Main,Vassal,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, why are you bowing down to your people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.07,0:24:24.24,Main,Vassal,0,0,0,,You mustn't! You are the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.24,0:24:25.65,Main,Vassal,0,0,0,,Please, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.65,0:24:27.53,Main,Vassal,0,0,0,,Raise your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:32.82,Main,Vassal,0,0,0,,If you're seen acting like this, you'll bring shame to your ancestors!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.82,0:24:34.96,Main,Vassal,0,0,0,,You'll become the whole world's laughing-stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.96,0:24:36.09,Main,Vassal,0,0,0,,Stop this, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.67,0:24:40.97,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,I beg of you! This is no joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.97,0:24:47.26,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,If you want proof of my sincerity, I'll gladly cut off my own hands or feet for you, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.43,0:24:51.82,Flashbacks,Riku,0,0,0,,Listen close, Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.33,0:24:57.27,Flashbacks,Riku,0,0,0,,Should the worst happen, I will at least try to take Doflamingo down myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.27,0:25:00.06,Flashbacks,Tank,0,0,0,,King Riku, isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.28,0:25:04.84,Flashbacks,Riku,0,0,0,,I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.05,0:25:11.22,Thoughts,Tank,0,0,0,,We must gather that money, whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.84,0:25:16.40,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Hurry up, everyone! Get your money, like the king asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.40,0:25:21.51,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,That's right!  The king is kind, he'd never do this for selfish reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.51,0:25:23.53,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's gotta have some good reason for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.53,0:25:25.82,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Bring all your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.82,0:25:28.15,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alright!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.43,0:25:53.92,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,This proves the king's greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.08,0:25:57.20,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.53,0:25:58.60,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.47,0:26:02.94,Thoughts,Tank,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.94,0:26:07.61,Thoughts,Tank,0,0,0,,People have wholeheartedly trusted the Riku Royal Family for 800 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.61,0:26:10.25,Thoughts,Tank,0,0,0,,What a magnificent kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.25,0:26:11.85,Thoughts,Tank,0,0,0,,This country will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.68,0:26:14.38,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,We will repay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.52,0:26:18.09,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Now carry the money back to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.09,0:26:19.58,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.58,0:26:20.99,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Commander Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.99,0:26:23.47,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,His Majesty is in the town of Sevio.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.47,0:26:24.70,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Look at the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.70,0:26:26.37,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.04,0:26:29.78,Captions,,0,0,180,,{\fad(500,400)}Southern Town Sevio
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.91,0:26:34.51,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Your Majesty. You didn't need to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.51,0:26:35.68,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.66,0:26:41.81,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,King Riku! We may not know what your reasons are, but we believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.20,0:26:43.40,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Run away! {Why would you have two lines in a row with the same dialogue be translated different ways? O_O}{Xemnas: Well "run, run, run" over and over again gets tedious and the last one is extended.}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.60,0:26:47.37,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,King Riku! What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.17,0:27:03.45,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.81,0:27:13.14,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,King Riku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.88,0:27:20.75,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,No! Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.75,0:27:22.86,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,King Riku, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.86,0:27:24.12,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.12,0:27:26.45,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Move! Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.45,0:27:28.66,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.98,0:27:32.45,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,He's even killing the soldiers?!{can't the timing be a bit longer}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.13,0:27:38.07,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,My body's moving on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.67,0:27:42.28,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,What... is going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.28,0:27:43.97,Main,Tank,0,0,0,,King Riku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.82,0:27:51.42,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.42,0:27:53.85,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,What a horrible king!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.85,0:27:56.79,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,The night is still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.79,0:28:00.33,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Now, soldiers! You dance too!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.47,0:28:04.99,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Parasite!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.78,0:28:10.18,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Now the soldiers have gone insane too!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.00,0:28:12.25,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.73,0:28:15.44,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,C-Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.44,0:28:17.74,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,King Riku, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.74,0:28:20.18,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,He's never done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.28,0:28:24.31,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Is it something we did?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.93,0:28:28.23,Thoughts,Riku,0,0,0,,There is no excuse for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.23,0:28:31.34,Thoughts,Riku,0,0,0,,The country is done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.77,0:28:35.34,Thoughts,Riku,0,0,0,,This was Doflamingo's trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.34,0:28:38.31,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,What has happened to you, Your Majesty!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.31,0:28:39.80,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.31,0:28:44.37,Main,Trebol,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Can we start now, Doffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.98,0:28:47.95,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Don't be so impatient, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.56,0:28:53.76,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,We will wait until the country has been plunged into the very depths of despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.76,0:28:57.08,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,and they curse King Riku with all their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.78,0:29:01.48,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,That is when the heroes will appear!
